rows.label: tlk70000131_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Awww, Milt and Satahiko
aren't with you?

rows.label: tlk70000131_04_msg0003
rows.name:
They're watching over stuff
in the capital, huh? That's
important, I guess.

rows.label: tlk70000131_04_msg0004
rows.name:
But I still wanna play
with them again...

rows.label: tlk70000131_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Maybe my dad'll take me with him
to the city if I ask real loud!
